Hello,
I would like to discuss the commission further. According to my statistics,
the total commission is currently nearly $2,000, however, I have only
received just over $700 so far. I hope you can help me check and support me
with the remaining commission when convenient, so that I can continue to
optimize my advertising and have a long-term partnership with your company.
Thank you very much and I look forward to your reply soon.
